Title: 整体架构图
Describe: 运行时、发布包和外部系统的层次边界。
------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
S04_ARCHITECTURE - 分层架构

[Description]
Deep Agents 把 SDK 作为中心层，周边入口按用途分成 deployment、terminal UI、protocol adapter、sandbox providers 和 evaluation harness。

[UML]
@startuml
left to right direction
actor "Developer" as Dev
actor "ACP Client" as Client
cloud "LangGraph Platform" as Platform
cloud "LangSmith API" as Smith
node "Terminal" as Terminal

package "Entry packages" {
  component "deepagents-cli" as DeployCLI
  component "deepagents-code" as CodeCLI
  component "deepagents-acp" as ACP
}
package "Core SDK" {
  component "create_deep_agent" as Create
  component "Middleware stack" as MW
  component "Backends" as Backends
  component "Profiles" as Profiles
}
package "Extensions" {
  component "Partner sandboxes" as Sandboxes
  component "QuickJS middleware" as Quick
  component "Evals and Harbor" as Evals
}

Dev --> DeployCLI : init deploy agents mcp-servers
Dev --> CodeCLI : dcode session
Client --> ACP : protocol requests
DeployCLI --> Smith : managed agent API
DeployCLI --> Platform : directory and deployment
CodeCLI --> Terminal : Textual UI
CodeCLI --> Create
ACP --> Create
Evals --> Create
Create --> MW
Create --> Backends
Create --> Profiles
Sandboxes --> Backends
Quick --> MW
@enduml

[Detail]
入口层的 `deepagents-cli` 只做部署相关命令，见 `libs/cli/deepagents_cli/main.py:151-167`；`deepagents-code` 是终端交互包，`libs/code/pyproject.toml` 声明 Textual、LangGraph SDK、MCP、sandbox 和 model provider 依赖；`deepagents-acp` 用 `AgentServerACP` 接 ACP 客户端，见 `server.py:92-103`。核心 SDK 层集中在 `libs/deepagents`：`create_deep_agent` 负责 middleware stack、backend、profile 和 LangGraph compiled graph。外部系统边界包括 LangSmith API、LangGraph Platform、terminal UI、ACP client 和各 sandbox provider。维护时应先判断改动位于入口、SDK 核心、协议适配还是 provider 扩展，避免把周边包特定逻辑推入 SDK。
